OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy start with showers or
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain. Then
OL,7,Fbrightening up from the west with
OL,8,Fscattered showers, most frequent in
OL,9,Fthe west. Fresh to strong west or
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds, but gales in
OL,11,Fnorth at first.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night
OL,14,Fwith rain spreading from the west,
OL,15,Fturning heavy across the northwest.
OL,16,FDrier around Nairn. Windy with strong
OL,17,Fto gale southwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
