OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FHeavy rain clearing away
OL,6,Fthrough the morning followed by bright
OL,7,Fspells and showers. Snow on hills.
OL,8,FStrong southwesterly winds, gales
OL,9,Falong the west coast later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold
OL,12,Fwith bright spells and wintry showers
OL,13,Fon Friday and Saturday, Further rain
OL,14,Ffollowed by showers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
